## English

radiation
n.辐射
Don't get close to radiation if you are not in a protective suit.

mild
adj.清淡的;温暖的;轻微的
I would love a bowl of mild chicken soup right now.

opt
vi.选择
She opted for music class because she just wasn't interested in any others.

peg
n.晾衣架
v.限定(价格、工资等)
I use pegs to make sure my washing stays on the line.

incorporate
v.包含;使并入
The app update incorporate many new features and improvements.

pioneer
n.先锋,先驱
vt.开辟,首倡
He's a pioneer in climbing, that is, the first man to reach the summit.

wage
n.工资,薪水
vt.开展,进行(战争、运动)
The worker was so happy when she got her wages.

rear
adj.背面的
n.后部
v.抚养
I could only see a tree in my rear-view mirror.

swamp
n.沼泽
v.使困惑,压倒
Crocodiles often live in swamps.

dean
n.(大学的)学院院长;系主任;牧师
The dean of our department is reading in his office.

distortion
n.扭曲,变形
He is laughing at the distortion of his reflection.

patriotism
n.爱国主义,爱国心,爱国精神
He has a strong sense of patriotism.

## leetcode

2455. Average Value of Even Numbers That Are Divisible by Three

```go
func averageValue(nums []int) int {
    sum, cnt := 0, 0
	for _, num := range nums {
        if num % 2 == 0 && num % 3 == 0 {
            sum += num
            cnt++
        }
    }
    if cnt == 0 {
        return 0
    }
    return sum/cnt
}
```
